testcaseName: Child under 9 received only one in first season
generalDescription: This test case describes when a child under the age of 9 receives only one influenza dose in his first season, that a second dose is recommended at 4 weeks later.
reasonForChange:
V4.4: Rolled test cases forward from 2019-2020 season to 2020-2021 season.
V4.1: Rolled test cases forward from 2018-2019 season to 2019-2020 season.
V3.5: Rolled test cases forward from 2017-18 season to 2018-19 season.
